title: 115. The What, Why And How Of Self-Awareness
itunes:title: 115. The What, Why And How Of Self-Awareness
description:
Real winners are extremely self-aware. They know what they are good at and the areas they need to improve. On today's episode, Andy explains why understanding self-awareness is critical to your success and the steps to become self-aware to dominate in business and life.
